title: Loki - Brother of Thor
description:
Loki- Brother of Thor is a fan-made film by Loki Odinson on Vimeo.

It takes footage from Thor, Thor 2, The Avengers, Guardians of the Galaxy, plus deleted scenes of the above movies, and test footage and edits it all together to show the Marvel Cinematic Universe from the eyes of Loki.

The movie is 2:15:48 long in standard definition.

Enjoy, and keep seeding.
